The wireless pulse oximeter is a reliable way to spot-check blood oxygen saturation (spo2) and pulse rate (bpm). This lightweight and portable device takes fast noninvasive measurements at the fingertip. Track and view your spo2 and bpm readings directly on the device?s display and in the ihealth spo2 app during sports training or other recreational activities.
